1
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,400
Based on the location Hu Mei described,

2
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,600
it should be this room.

3
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,080
Let's go.

4
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,640
Time of death was 2 a.m. precisely last night.

5
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,880
A straw doll was stuffed into his abdomen.

6
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,720
Although the modus operandi matches the previous two victims,

7
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:30,960
judging from Liu Quan's body,

8
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,120
and the dozen or so stab wounds,

9
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,200
the killer was clearly venting anger.

10
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,000
In that case,

11
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,720
these three were killed by the same person.

12
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,080
It was all to avenge Jin Yue.

13
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,240
But Jin Yue is already dead.

14
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,200
And the three men related to her are all dead too.

15
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,080
Who could the killer be?

16
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,560
It matches her clothing size.

17
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:03,520
What are you muttering about?

18
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:09,400
Hmm?

19
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,000
Lao Yao.

20
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:12,840
Yeah?

21
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,640
Jin Yue might not be dead.

22
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:16,640
What?

23
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,720
Do you remember

24
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,880
when we parted ways with Chen Lian?

25
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,760
At the end of the Hour of the Rat yesterday.

26
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,760
The timing matches.

27
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,760
After she separated from us,

28
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,960
she found Liu Quan,

29
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,440
and killed him.

30
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,600
You mean,

31
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,120
Chen Lian killed him?

32
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:33,960
No.

33
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,360
It was Jin Yue.

34
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,040
Could it be...

35
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,440
Shentu.

36
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,000
This case...

37
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,600
do we still need to investigate further?

38
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,280
The closer we get to the truth,

39
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,560
the more afraid you become.

40
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,880
Knowing what this woman has been through...

41
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,040
The Dali Temple must uphold justice.

42
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:02,360
If the killer really is that woman,

43
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,120
then I think what she did was justice.

44
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,520
I can't bear to arrest her.

45
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,920
If you can't bear it,

46
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,960
tragedies like this will surely happen again.

47
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,800
If we make the truth public,

48
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,240
those wife-pawners

49
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,000
and wife-renters

50
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,880
will surely be deterred.

51
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,240
Lao Yao.

52
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:24,440
Yeah.

53
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,080
We are doing this for the sake of more people.

54
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:32,600
Guiyi.

55
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,200
Go to the Tian residence.

56
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,360
Keep a close watch on Chen Lian.

57
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:36,640
Okay.

58
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,800
You're back.

59
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,120
Yeah.

60
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,200
I'm back.

61
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,160
Let's eat.

62
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:11,040
Look.

63
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,400
It's you.

64
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,200
Yeah.

65
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,400
It looks quite like me.

66
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,160
Am I pretty,

67
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,400
or is she pretty?

68
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,120
They are both you.

69
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,280
Both are pretty.

70
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,040
Why are you a fool?

71
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,520
Why are you a fool?

72
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:57,920
Lady Jin Yue.

73
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,320
You guessed it.

74
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,160
I didn't expect Hu Ya

75
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:09,920
to carve so exquisitely.

76
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,120
Indeed.

77
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,960
Although he is a fool,

78
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,560
his heart seems

79
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,800
clearer than anyone else's.

80
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,560
He...

81
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,600
is the only person in this world

82
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,400
who treats me well.

83
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,200
You're not happy.

84
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,080
I will make a figurine

85
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,720
to make you happy.

86
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,680
You are pretty.

87
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,280
I'll make a pretty figurine.

88
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,880
My son is a fool.

89
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,520
He's useless.

90
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:23,040
How could he know

91
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,080
how to give the Hu family

92
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,080
heirs to carry on the line?

93
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:28,480
You...

94
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,720
what do you mean?

95
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,200
I spent so much money

96
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,320
to buy you into this family.

97
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,120
And the pawn term is only one year.

98
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,000
The time is almost up.

99
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,760
I can't let my money go down the drain.

100
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,520
As long as you get pregnant,

101
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,360
it's the Hu family's seed.

102
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:00,720
No!

103
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,000
Let me go!

104
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,000
Let me go!

105
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,240
Not only was I pawned,

106
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,320
but after suffering such humiliation,

107
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,480
Liu Quan didn't think to stand up for me.

108
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,240
Instead, he used it as leverage

109
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,400
to demand money from Hu Pin.

110
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,160
One person is one share of money.

111
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,960
Two people are two shares of money.

112
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:52,680
These words...

113
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,520
were spoken by Liu Quan.

114
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,080
But Hu Pin was unwilling to pay again.

115
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,840
So he came up with a plan.

116
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,400
He pawned me again to Tian Wan.

117
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,280
Liu Quan agreed.

118
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,680
He agreed.

119
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,640
Brother Tian.

120
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,440
This little lady's hips...

121
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:29,240
look like the perfect mold for bearing sons.

122
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,280
Even I'm envious looking at them.

123
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:34,240
That can't be wrong.

124
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,480
She just bore a child for my family.

125
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,520
It was a little boy.

126
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,680
White and chubby.

127
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:40,240
With a handle.

128
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,440
With a handle.

129
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:43,960
How about it, Brother Tian?

130
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,760
Such good stock isn't easy to find.

131
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,760
Look at these hips.

132
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,400
Why don't you...

133
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,720
inspect her?

134
00:08:59,640 --> 00:08:59,800
Done.

135
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:01,280
It's a deal.

136
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,240
Pawning this wife for one year.

137
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:03,960
Fifty strings.

138
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:04,560
Come.

139
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:06,960
Sign here.

140
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,400
Good.

141
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:21,160
It's done.

142
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,080
Even Chen Lian,

143
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,600
was pawned to the Tian family too.

144
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,520
The pawn term ended,

145
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,840
but no one came to redeem her.

146
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,480
She just waited and waited.

147
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,920
That night by the river,

148
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,120
she saved me.

149
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,440
Before she died,

150
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,360
she entrusted her two children to me.

151
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,640
The infant is already at Dali Temple.

152
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,080
Dali Temple will raise him.

153
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,640
If fate allows in the future,

154
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:18,840
you will surely meet again.

155
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,640
The Jin Yue of the past is gone.

156
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,720
Find a place where no one knows you,

157
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,200
and start over.

158
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,640
The criminal Jin Yue,

159
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:14,880
has committed grave sins.

160
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:16,760
According to the law, she should be beheaded.

161
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,880
But considering the circumstances,

162
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,240
she is granted leniency.

163
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,080
The death penalty is waived,

164
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,040
but punishment cannot be escaped.

165
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,320
She is hereby sentenced to exile in Jiangnan Circuit.

166
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,560
As a warning to others.

167
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,280
I hope they can find a place undisturbed by others,

168
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,480
and start a new life.

169
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,320
I also pray that people in this world

170
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,920
can show women more compassion,

171
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:44,280
and no longer let them

172
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,120
suffer such hardships.
